{"tid":1524321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[同我推撚爆佢！]無論你係咩角色都適合既香港國際機場交通攻略","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T01:37:54.000Z","uid":43668,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"76f2bc6d18cef1e4c378a1fa2ae944e4372a8707","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"〔過牆梯〕淆底唔敢入機場既同我入黎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512735</a><br />\n<blockquote>之前有巴打開po講過，其實要塞機場唔止要令旅客上唔到機，更重要既係︰<br />\n1. 要令機場返工既人<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">返唔到工</span></strong><br />\n2. 要令夜晚至凌晨時份既<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">貨運時段出唔到貨</span></strong><br />\n咁既然機場有禁制令，令有人會因為怕犯禁制令而唔敢入，咁不如塞出少少，塞其他樽頸位仲好。（完全唔反對而且好讚成有人照入機場塞，各有各做。我地塞出少少機場巴打撤都有個照應。）而去機場既車路樽頸位有兩個check point︰<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">青馬大橋</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">東涌</span></strong>，外加一條<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">機場快線</span></strong>。記住要塞唔係一定要100%塞死先有用，只要登機人數太少航班就要cancel，所以做到~90%限流就好夠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: teal;\">1. 青馬大橋</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n如果塞到青馬大橋基本上機場貨運就癱瘓（除非用水路，但係機場島冇貨運碼頭，所以好難用到水路），客運都會嚴重受阻，得返搭鐵（或者搭船去梅窩愉景灣再轉車，但係呢個方法極唔方便同低效率，可以由佢）。<br />\n點塞？紅隧都塞到，用返同一個方法塞咪得。<br />\n又或者再比多少少創意︰<br />\n<blockquote>【女司機隧道收費亭入錯線！竟在自動繳費亭落車付錢？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2368107/%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E4%BA%AD%E5%85%A5%E9%8C%AF%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%81%E7%AB%9F%E5%9C%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB%E4%BA%AD%E8%90%BD%E8%BB%8A%E4%BB%98%E9%8C%A2%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2368107%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%259A%25A7%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E4%25BA%25AD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%258C%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A%25EF%25BC%2581%25E7%25AB%259F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25B9%25B3%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E4%25BA%25AD%25E8%2590%25BD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25BB%2598%25E9%258C%25A2%25EF%25BC%259F&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=bf894e65\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2368107/%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E4%BA%AD%E5%85%A5%E9%8C%AF%E7%B7%9A%EF%BC%81%E7%AB%9F%E5%9C%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB%E4%BA%AD%E8%90%BD%E8%BB%8A%E4%BB%98%E9%8C%A2%EF%BC%9F</a><br />\n【每日一片：過隧道入錯線？ 失魂司機直衝收費亭】<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190813/bkn-20190813115654357-0813_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190813%2Fbkn-20190813115654357-0813_00822_001.html&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=46f77bde\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190813/bkn-20190813115654357-0813_00822_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n再唔係，可以用返舊方法P牌仔<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">慢駛</span></span></strong>、收費亭<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">落車數散紙</span></span></strong>。總之呼籲各位有車人士入大嶼山自駕遊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">2. 東涌</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n（東涌而家個情況有D尷尬，因為而家有埋港珠澳大橋人工島，果邊又有多條路入機場，所以塞到東涌都塞唔哂，不過都照講住先）<br />\n東涌過機場有兩條路︰<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>赤鱲角南路</strong></span>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>北大嶼山公路</strong></span>。兩條都係橋，塞到就完哂，問題係點塞？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8cE13L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8cE13L.png&h=77679ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖係東涌連接機場島既地圖（左上係機場島），圖入面分別用<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>同<span style=\"color: orange;\">橙色</span>mark起左兩條路，仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>點同<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>點。<br />\n要塞<span style=\"color: orange;\">赤鱲角南路</span>比較易，只需要塞到<span style=\"color: orange;\">B</span>點圈住個迴旋處就得，用咩方法塞大家自己諗，果度同普通馬路冇分別雜物好人好車好自己諗。<br />\n另外一邊要塞<span style=\"color: red;\">北大嶼山公路</span>條橋就有D煩，因為大家由地圖上面見到其實果條路係由青馬果邊直接過黎既高速公路，唔似得普通馬路咁可以比你無啦啦停或者比人行落去。所以要塞就要喺<span style=\"color: red;\">A</span>點度塞，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">塞公路上面個迴旋處然後倒灌車龍落返公路</span></strong></span>。<br />\n其實呢個情況喺北區成日出現，住北區既巴絲可以Verify到。<br />\n<blockquote>【上水交通癱瘓4粒鐘 司機市民「嗌救命」】<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/bkn-20180307193907252-0307_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180307%2Fbkn-20180307193907252-0307_00822_001.html&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=a14bebbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180307/bkn-20180307193907252-0307_00822_001.html</a></blockquote><br />\n北區、上水成日塞車塞到交通癱瘓、倒灌返入粉嶺公路都係因為迴旋處塞（下圖紅點），好多時係冇交通意外都會無啦啦塞。而東涌去機場既佈局同北區好似，所以可以用返同樣策略塞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nfay6Dw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfay6Dw.png&h=7a896fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">3. 塞鐵</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n地鐵不合作運動仲洗人教？<br />\n如果唔想比人嘈既，直接搵多D人買飛坐爆機鐵佢（冇咁易比人趕但係會比好多錢黨鐵賺，自己斟酌），不停遊車河。又或者大家發揮下創意用自己既方法唔比佢開車，唔比人去到機場，亦唔比人出到市區。<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多 901機場見<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1d5137c18540033c022cee650a6a789636384586","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:34.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 1/10"},{"pid":"6b0104b0f33c531deb3b258aaab1ef1e7906f159","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:05:05.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 2/10"},{"pid":"a36aa58eee5ec818d770106a23ad84a41d6dd27e","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 3/10"},{"pid":"d3cf1a4c359b5b32c341ffc7131405413304e6a5","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 4/10"},{"pid":"19eeb6b518fbe0b9581708af357b197aa0f5be51","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 5/10"},{"pid":"df8acb087ea4b0eebde1fce12248798bd8e67339","tid":1524321,"uid":139964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"273f8d5ee4b6768832400f18cf30a7808895b43c","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:12:34.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 6/10"},{"pid":"6fced1a1e7abbb052ac235add2ac65ab061e79ba","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 7/10"},{"pid":"043f0c3451a537dad01032f9019d76698d090edb","tid":1524321,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"9月1, 1300機場<br />\n你知點做未? 未知就睇啦 <span style=\"color: red;\">(圖一係重點)</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自由服飾, 唔洗黑衫, 帶埋個GIP, 免口號, 免傳單<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsAjL4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsAjL4W.jpg&h=f128e56d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sSCuoRC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsSCuoRC.jpg&h=6422114b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYxKcKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYxKcKY.jpg&h=b37e07ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2a1e4321fa6fb15e9133addd32fa1cd3b547c1e","tid":1524321,"uid":139173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:15:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JpJpXcD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJpJpXcD.jpg&h=3a485f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n⚠️提提大家⚠️<br />\n聽日千祈唔好入機場室內禁制區範圍<br />\n藐視法庭 可以令你入獄幾個月"},{"pid":"7ed1a79f887e0f26f7a7a1fed180da6d540e8d2d","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:15:47.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 8/10"},{"pid":"db16307b7008d9f6ee8c9dfd5b432b350f34b08e","tid":1524321,"uid":120040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<br />\n和理非出動嘅時候到了 你唔係忍到今日手足為你犧牲呀?"},{"pid":"b9dc15c52b715845a205983586874650a67ab309","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 9/10"},{"pid":"a9ed81efd270a8a31e1a7998cc25167f4455b79a","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 10/10"},{"pid":"5ff5061e87ff3ebbd0f7064b61e381af32a01957","tid":1524321,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"[連登公投] 同我拆哂黨鐵佢好唔好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d442082d5a3b1dda0e870264cd66b46376308534","tid":1524321,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:19:51.000Z","msg":"行動post推"},{"pid":"10cfe432fd36942a74768eed7001bbdf060112de","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d442082d5a3b1dda0e870264cd66b46376308534","tid":1524321,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:19:51.000Z","msg":"行動post推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:20:03.000Z","msg":"op..."},{"pid":"6bf6d5443f55bc32e5ec963071b6d96af3377f1f","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 11/10"},{"pid":"e0e9669791b9b1962f2e4e3a79edb2c66336c105","tid":1524321,"uid":45600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:22:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7168201a24426c06db1f34263b960dbf4dea46ce","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:22:29.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 12/10"},{"pid":"284c12850202e4d1e27843b40fa9d427978998af","tid":1524321,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:23:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.liveatc.net/search/?icao=VHHH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liveatc.net%2Fsearch%2F%3Ficao%3DVHHH&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70gRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=56a8ae10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liveatc.net/search/?icao=VHHH</a><br />\n第一手資料得知航班情況<br />\n應該係聽VHHH Tower/VHHH Tower (South)<br />\n有錯請指正"},{"pid":"57634518bb35aed3f99d097563c752954d2ef090","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 13/10"},{"pid":"f1bc28ff6aef5065c4ddf9ea18fb310bcd927923","tid":1524321,"uid":43668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:26:34.000Z","msg":"屌你自推10次 14/10"},{"pid":"5f78858140082f1933a1810a4d336c062fae78af","tid":1524321,"uid":222451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e59P8v3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe59P8v3.jpg&h=4577f61c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1AsaKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1AsaKo.jpg&h=5c61cb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請轉至Twitter同Reddit"}]}